data.title: Cambridge University Reporter Special
data.text:
Grace submitted to the Regent House on 23 July 2009

The Council submits the following Grace to the Regent House. This Grace, unless it is withdrawn or a ballot is requested in accordance with the regulations for Graces of the Regent House (Statutes and Ordinances, p. 107), will be deemed to have been approved at 4 p.m. on Friday, 31 July 2009.
